Bhopal disaster (1984): toxic gas leak at pesticide plant
Beirut explosion (2020): ammonium nitrate explosion at port

Atomic Age
- Nuclear weapon (1945)
- Nuclear power plant (1954): core meltdown, Red Forest
- Chernobyl disaster (1986)
- Fukushima disaster (2011): tsunami

Space exploration
- Artificial sattelite (Sputnik, Laika) [1957]
- Astronaut, Vostok (Yuri Gagarin) [1961]
- Moon landing, Apollo 11 (Neil Armstrong, Buzz Aldrin) [1969]
- Interstellar (Voyager) [1977]
- Space Shuttle Challenger disaster [1986]: launch
- Hubble Space Telescope [1990]
- Space Shuttle Columbia disaster [2003]: reentry
- James Webb Space Telescope [2022]

Modular space station
- Mir (1996): USSR, continuously inhabited, decommission in 2001
- ISS / International Space Station (2000): continuously inhabited
- Tiangong (2021): China

Digital Revolution (1947-now)
- Laser (1960)
- Transistor, Computer
- Internet, Email, Social media
- Smartphone
- Data, Algorithm
- Artificial intelligence

Fermilab
- Tevatron (1983-2011): particle accelerator, near Chicago
CERN
- Large Hadron Collider (LHC, 2010): particle collider, near Geneva

